Steps to correctly install BCISystem:
1) create a python environment (eg. conda env) with python=3.8 (help: conda cheat sheet)
2) activate the new env
3) pip install matplotlib tensorflow sklearn pandas mne pylsl

Windows: problems with numpy 1.19.4. Fix comes around 2021 jan. Until then install 1.19.3

Now you can use the BCISystem... =)

If you have any problems you can contact:
- Csaba Köllőd: kollod.csaba@itk.ppke.hu
